headline.print_headline: Phelps Into 200 IM Final at Pan Pacs; Lochte Out
headline.main: Phelps Into 200 IM Final at Pan Pacs; Lochte Out

headline.print_headline: Ivory Coast Shuts Borders With Liberia, Guinea Over Ebola Threat
